Jordan Flake handles all aspects of Nevada probate — from straightforward administrations to complex, contested estates. His approach is methodical, transparent, and always focused on achieving the best outcome for the family.

Whether you're an executor unsure of your obligations, a beneficiary who believes a will is invalid, or a family member trying to navigate an intestate estate, Jordan has the experience to guide you through every step of the process.
